How to Use
Install Dependencies:

Ensure you have Node.js installed to run the script above for creating the files.
Run the script in a terminal to generate the index.html and wallet.js files.
Serve the Files:

Place the generated files in a web server directory (e.g., use tools like Live Server or http-server).
Test the Wallet:

Open the index.html file in your browser.
Connect to MetaMask and interact with the wallet.
